comments.body:
> +1 the ability to easily apply a `render` prop to custom components would be a major QOL upgrade IMO.

@adamfratino If you are interested in trying this out, there's now an open PR with a POC and a sandbox for a `useRenderer` hook that will let you do exactly this: https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/1418
We discussed this among the team and decided that a hook may be a better abstraction than `<Slot/>`
